<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/710347-does-the-fact-that-this-author-is">Does the fact that this Author is Protestant not Catholic affect how you perceive the credibility of his protagonist or explain the inconsistencies and lack of voracity the way the history of this politically charged struggle for national autonomy is portrayed?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_710347'><a id="like_count_community_question_710347" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/710347?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F13008754-the-cold-cold-ground">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/710347-does-the-fact-that-this-author-is">5 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/710347-does-the-fact-that-this-author-is">See all 4 answers</a>
</li>
</ul>
