<span id="freeTextContainer8308342107854024846">Now i am going to read this series. Hope it is fun! The last detective books that i have read were Sherlock Holmes books. It will be interesting to se</span>
  <span id="freeText8308342107854024846" style="display:none">Now i am going to read this series. Hope it is fun! The last detective books that i have read were Sherlock Holmes books. It will be interesting to see how detective literature has evolved over more than 100 years.</span>
  <a data-text-id="8308342107854024846" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

    <br/>

    <span class="xhrCommentFooter greyText">
